products.title: Ecowood, Porcelain Grey Satin - Venetian Blind
products.description: The ecowood in porcelain grey satin is a pretty yet unassuming piece in a pale dove grey and with a smooth, silky finish. This attractive blind is practical and durable, as well as offering style and sophistication to any room in the home. As for the colour? It matches everything. Give your lounge a contemporary makeover by opting for an ultra-trendy yellow and grey colour scheme. Paint one wall in a sunny yellow tone and the others in a soft white.

products.title: Origin, Hunter Green - Venetian Blind
products.description: Dark and unusual, the origin in hunter green offers a perfect satin finish on slim aluminium slats, within a matching frame, and controlled using coordinating pull-cords, making this the perfect blind for both pleasure and function. For a country aesthetic with a modern twist, work the hunter green into a warm kitchen colour scheme, complementing with terracottas, soft yellows, and creams. Or make a real statement in a contemporary living room by placing it against white walls and light-coloured woods.

products.title: Ecowood, Driftwood Fine Grain - Venetian Blind
products.description: The ecowood in driftwood fine grain is a prettily textured piece in a light, natural wood tone, and with a realistic wood look. A practical and hardwearing blind that's simple and easy to use, it will look pretty and natural wherever it's placed. Create a simple yet elegantly organic scheme in a dining room by including naked woods and artisan fabrics as well as the lovely driftwood fine grain. Go for stark white walls and plenty of plant-life, adding bamboo accessories to add to the look.

products.title: Ecowood, Saddle Satin - Venetian Blind
products.description: Saddle satin is the latest addition to their celebrated ecowood range. With a gentle cream that sits gently in the background you'll have the perfect compliment to the bolder colours that really bring your home to life. No matter what you have in mind the secret is to let your creativity run wild. Don't put limits on it; think about how you can get dark greys into the mix and how satin will allow them to take centre stage.

products.title: Wow Factor, Brushed Azure - Venetian Blind
products.description: The wow factor in brushed azure is a muted silver with just the faintest hint of blue and it will rest discreetly against your window frame. Control the light in the room easily by using the pull-cords to adjust the position of the aluminium slats, moving and tilting them at will. The brushed azure will provide any window with a hushed metallic look so that bolder features in the room can take centre stage.

products.title: Wow Factor, Harmony Star - Venetian Blind
products.description: The gorgeous bronze-gold of the wow factor harmony star is eye-catching and pronounced, without being overly bold, and its shimmering glitter is discreet, catching the light - and the eye - whenever the light hits it. Add quirky luxury to your living room by placing the harmony star against deep chocolates and cappuccino creams, letting the blind take centre stage. Or let it claim the limelight in a neutral hallway or landing instead, to add a little sparkle as you get home.

products.description: The impressions fauxwood range is stylish and sumptuous. This solid white wooden blind is a great way to add more character to any space. Slats of the blind come with a bit of texture. At swift direct blinds, quality is important to us, not only does this faux wooden blinds come with a fabulous five year guarantee, but customer-first service and industry-leading delivery times. products.title: Wow Factor, Brushed Platinum - Venetian Blind
products.description: Metallic and eye-catching, the wow factor in brushed platinum combines functional utilitarianism with a subtle, luxury sheen, on a blind whose aluminium slats are easily adjusted to allow for changes in light and privacy needs. Complement a blue colour scheme in the home office or guest bedroom, accenting with matching ornaments, or simply use to add a metallic neutral to a bold, bright dining room, den, or living room, where cosy greens or deep plum purples might take centre stage.

products.title: Wow Factor, Carmela Star - Venetian Blind
products.description: The wow factor in carmela star is a soft, barely-there gold with gently shimmering glitter, on firm aluminium slats, creating a pretty, metallic effect. When closed, enjoy all the privacy and shelter of the dark, but when open, light will seep through in varying amounts, depending on your positioning of the slats. Pair with browns and golds for a luxurious feel in the living or dining room, or use as a standout statement feature in your bedroom, set against white walls.

products.title: Wow Factor, Brushed Oyster - Venetian Blind
products.description: Sophisticated and discreet, the wow factor in brushed oyster is a classic brushed gold that combines class and subtlety. Crafted from durable, heavy gauge aluminium slats that are easy to tilt and move about, this is a blind that is built to last - in quality and style. For subdued glamour, use with dark navy blues, deep purples, or rich burgundys, accenting occasionally with pretty creams. These would all make flexible colour schemes, perfect in many rooms, including the living room, dining room, and master bedroom.

products.title: Wow Factor, Gunmetal Star - Venetian Blind
products.description: Slate grey works effortlessly with a gentle shimmer to create the pretty but utilitarian window covering that is the wow factor in gunmetal star. By blending a high quality, heavy gauge aluminium metal with simple pull-cords to control the light, this blind offers a durable and long-lasting window covering that will retain its quality and style. Hang the gunmetal star in a contemporary dining room, accented by bright silvers, or use in a teenager's room for a fun and exciting shimmering window covering, sat amongst soft greys and dulled whites.

products.title: Wow Factor, Silver Star - Venetian Blind
products.description: A pretty, shimmering blind, patterned with a soft glitter, the wow factor in silver star is soft and unobtrusive. The heavy-duty aluminium slats can be adjusted to allow just the right amount of light into the room, all controlled by easy-to-use pull-cords. Pretty pink bedrooms with a light and romantic feel will benefit from the silver star, which will glisten beautifully amongst white walls and hushed rose hues.

products.title: Impressions Gloss White Faux Wood
products.description: Their impressions faux wooden blinds are a perfect option for bathrooms and kitchens as not only are these faux woods flame retardant, they're also moisture-resistant. This luxurious gloss white faux wood created a clean and sophisticated feel whilst the gloss finish reflects light for a truly sleek finished look, a great options for rooms that recieve ample natural light. At swift direct blinds, quality is important to us, not only does this faux wooden blinds come with a fabulous five year guarantee, but customer-first service and industry-leading delivery times.

products.title: Ecowood, Antique Silver Satin - Venetian Blind
products.description: The beautifully grey-toned antique silver satin, from the faux wood ecowood range, has a distinctly vintage feel to it. Smooth, with light grain detailing, it offers sleek durability as well as tons of character and aesthetic appeal. Treat your master bedroom to a pretty vintage scheme, settling the antique silver satin against dusky pink walls and furnishing the room with subtle off-whites and dove greys.

products.title: Broody Aluminium Venetian
products.description: Black as the night, this venetian blind will standout and give a crisp, smart finish to any window. Use in your bathroom or kichen, or alongside a black and white themed room to finish the room off. Venetian blinds give you full control over the light entering your home with the raise and tilt controls. Keep your blinds looking their best with their easy to wipe clean aluminium slats, just use a damp cloth to wipe away any dirt or stains.

products.title: Latino Aluminium Venetian
products.description: Keep your blinds looking their best with their easy to wipe clean aluminium slats, just use a damp cloth to wipe away any dirt or stains. Raise and lower your blind to the perfect height, and then angle the venetian slats to control the light entering your home. All of their blinds are sold with built-in child safety mechanisms. We adhere to the guidelines set out by the british blind and shutter association and take safety extremely seriously.
